org.joonegap
Class WeightGene

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--org.joonegap.WeightGene
public class WeightGene
extends java.lang.Object

This Gene is used to model individual weights (or bias') in the neural network.

It can take any double value, and in all respects is very similar to a DoubleGene, except that it is initialised with a uniform random distribution ranging over [-0.5, 0.5]
